OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto two years and three months in youth
OL,8,Fdetention by Jersey's Royal Court
OL,9,Fafter admitting a series of offences
OL,10,Finvolving knives.
OL,12,FThe teenager, who cannot be named for
OL,13,Flegal reasons due to his age,
OL,14,Fattempted to rob a St Brelade resident
OL,15,Fand separately took a large serrated
OL,16,Fkitchen knife to Haute Vallee School -
OL,17,Fwhere he gained access to the
OL,18,Fcafeteria before being tackled by a
OL,19,Fmember of staff.
OL,26,@xD@\rr
