CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FOne student suffered a minor hand
OL,7,Finjury, with those who jumped in
OL,8,Fpraised by police for "their swift and
OL,9,Fselfless actions, which undoubtedly
OL,10,Fprevented more serious harm".
OL,12,FThe Royal Court heard the defendant,
OL,13,Fwho was 14 at the time, entered Haute
OL,14,FVallee's canteen on Monday 9 February,
OL,15,Fcarrying a 21-centimetre bread knife
OL,16,Fwhile around 200 pupils were there
OL,17,Fduring their lunchtime break.
OL,26,@vD@Err
