OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FThe prosecution said he had gone there
OL,7,Flooking for another student following
OL,8,Fan earlier dispute and wanted to get
OL,9,F"revenge".
OL,11,FStaff rushed to restrain him as
OL,12,Ffrightened pupils tried to move out of
OL,13,Fthe way.
OL,15,FOne student suffered a minor hand
OL,16,Finjury during the struggle, but the
OL,17,FCourt heard the quick intervention
OL,18,Fprevented the situation from becoming
OL,19,Ffar more serious.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
