OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FThe school incident was part of a
OL,7,Fwider pattern of offending.
OL,9,FThe teenager also admitted to
OL,10,Fthreatening his father with a kitchen
OL,11,Fknife during an argument at home, and
OL,12,Fattempting to rob a woman at her flat
OL,13,Fby pointing a knife at her stomach and
OL,14,Fdemanding her car keys - she firmly
OL,15,Fshut the door and was uninjured.
OL,17,FHowever, she says she now keeps her
OL,18,Fblinds shut and is frightened to go
OL,19,Fout alone at night.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FThe defendant also admitted to an
OL,7,Fearlier assault at McDonald's, where
OL,8,Fanother teenager was repeatedly
OL,9,Fpunched following an online dispute.
OL,11,FThe prosecution argued his offending
OL,12,Fwas escalating and that only a
OL,13,Fcustodial sentence could protect the
OL,14,Fpublic.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FDefence lawyers said the sentence
OL,7,Fproposed was "crushingly long" for a
OL,8,Fchild, highlighting his age, lack of
OL,9,Fprevious convictions, ADHD diagnosis,
OL,10,Fand positive engagement with education
OL,11,Fand carpentry at Greenfields Youth
OL,12,FCentre.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, psychological reports
OL,15,Fpresented to the Court raised concerns
OL,16,Fabout the teenager's emotional
OL,17,Fvolatility, lack of remorse and the
OL,18,Frisk of future offending.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,FSentencing him to two years and three
OL,7,Fmonths in youth detention, the judge,
OL,8,FJersey Bailiff Robert MacRae,
OL,9,Fdescribed the offending as "incredibly
OL,10,Fserious", stating it will have long-
OL,11,Flasting effects on the school and
OL,12,Fother students.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,15,FChildren, Young People, Education and
OL,16,FSkills (CYPES) says: "The safety and
OL,17,Fwellbeing of children, young people
OL,18,Fand staff will always remain our
OL,19,Fabsolute priority.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,F"Incidents of this nature are
OL,7,Fextremely rare, but we recognise the
OL,8,Fimpact this case has had on students,
OL,9,Fstaff, families and the wider
OL,10,Fcommunity and remain committed to
OL,11,Fsupporting schools."
OL,13,FThe States of Jersey Police adds:
OL,14,F"Jersey does not face a widespread
OL,15,Fknife problem, but we will not be
OL,16,Fcomplacent and will continue to take
OL,17,Fproactive steps, alongside our
OL,18,Fpartners and the wider community, to
OL,19,Fkeep the island safe.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1779451870
OL,3,CBoy behind school knife attack and
OL,4,Cattempted robbery sentenced
OL,6,F"We would also like to commend the
OL,7,Fstaff at Haute Vallee School for their
OL,8,Fswift and selfless actions, which
OL,9,Fundoubtedly prevented more serious
OL,10,Fharm."
OL,12,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,13,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,14,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,15,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
